</section>
<section id="slide-org778f82b">
<h3 id="org778f82b">REDCAPE as a process model</h3>
<ol>
<li>Phenomena (observations) - EXPLAIN</li>
<li>Review findings - EXPLORE</li>
<li>Critique and test findings - REASON</li>
<li>Extract meaning - DESIGN</li>
<li>Communicate findings - COMMUNICATE</li>
<li>Act on findings - ACT</li>
<li>Extend findings to future - PREDICT</li>

</ol>

</section>
<section id="slide-org205d0cb">
<h3 id="org205d0cb">Weaknesses of REDCAPE</h3>
<ul>
<li>Not testable (no observables)</li>
<li>Not mutually exclusive</li>
<li>Not collectively exhaustive</li>
<li>Not validated (except examples)</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
